        <title>Secure the Capitol Act</title>
      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To prohibit offices of the legislative branch from entering into a contract for the provision of goods or services within the Capitol Complex with any contractor who does not participate in the basic pilot program for employment eligibility verification, and for other purposes.</title>
      </item>
